{
  "uuid": "c772ec0fa5a64b6a40984c581c8a1f96",
  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "FIELD ENGINEER",
  "description": "<p><strong>JOB TITLE: FIELD SERVICE TECHICIAN</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>$3000 - $4000 with relevant working experience.</li>\n  <li>Full Time </li>\n  <li>5 Day Week:   Mon - Fri  8.30am - 5.30pm</li>\n  <li>AWS, Medical &amp; Dental Benefits, Mobile Allowance</li>\n  <li>Overseas Training Provided</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Semiconductor Robots installation, calibration and troubleshoot in cleanroom.</li>\n  <li>Service of Autonomous Mobile Robot, Stocker, E-rack, E-84, RFID and etc.</li>\n  <li>Provide front line support for key field service activities in line with customer requirements.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Duties &amp; Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Installation, commissioning, calibration, testing, troubleshooting and modification of Autonomous Mobile Robot, E-rack, Stocker and etc. at customer locations.</li>\n  <li>Provide preventive maintenance and repair service at established procedures, techniques, tools, test equipment and replacement parts.</li>\n  <li>Establish and maintain a professional working relationship with customers and co-workers through team work.</li>\n  <li>Monitor product performance and report back to management feedback from customer's request.</li>\n  <li>Handle cumer complaints to management to address and prevent future issues.</li>\n  <li>Other ad hoc duties.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Candidates with  NiTEC/ ITC/ Diploma /Electrical /Electronic Mechatronic Engineering, or equivalent educational background.</li>\n  <li>Related experience in equipment installation and maintenance.</li>\n  <li>Self-motivated, meticulous, disciplined and strong team player with high integrity.</li>\n  <li>Able to work independently under minimum supervision.</li>\n  <li>Available to work after office hour, on weekends or standby duty if required.</li>\n  <li>Able to travel overseas within short notice.</li>\n</ul>",
